name 'computer-systems-preassessment-intro_v2-2025'
title 'Computer Systems and Devices Pre-Assessment'
markdown <<MARKDOWN
This assessment will help determine your prior knowledge about computer hardware, software, operating systems, troubleshooting, data processing, and emerging technologies.

- You are **not expected to know all the answers**! This is just to see what you already understand.
- Read each question carefully and **choose the best answer** based on what you know.
- There are **no penalties for incorrect answers**, so do your best!
MARKDOWN
